import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz';
import { Button } from '../';

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"button"}}>{`Button`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties"}}>{`Properties`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Button} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"sizes"}}>{`Sizes`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Button>Regular</Button>
<Button size="sm">Smaller</Button>
<Button size="xs">Extra Smaller</Button>`} __scope={{props,Button}}>
    <Button>
        Regular
    </Button>
    <Button size="sm">
        Smaller
    </Button>
    <Button size="xs">
        Extra Smaller
    </Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"color"}}>{`Color`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Button color="warning">Warning</Button>
<Button color="secondary">Secondary</Button>
<Button color="error">Error</Button>
<Button color="primary">Primary</Button>
<Button color="success">Success</Button>
<Button color="black">Black</Button>
<Button color="white">White</Button>`} __scope={{props,Button}}>
    <Button color="warning">
        Warning
    </Button>
    <Button color="secondary">
        Secondary
    </Button>
    <Button color="error">
        Error
    </Button>
    <Button color="primary">
        Primary
    </Button>
    <Button color="success">
        Success
    </Button>
    <Button color="black">
        Black
    </Button>
    <Button color="white">
        White
    </Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"bordered"}}>{`Bordered`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={3} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Button bordered color="warning">
  Warning
</Button>
<Button bordered color="secondary">
  Secondary
</Button>
<Button bordered color="error">
  Error
</Button>
<Button bordered color="primary">
  Primary
</Button>
<Button bordered color="success">
  Success
</Button>
<Button bordered color="black">
  Black
</Button>
<Button bordered color="white">
  White
</Button>`} __scope={{props,Button}}>
    <Button bordered color="warning">
        Warning
    </Button>
    <Button bordered color="secondary">
        Secondary
    </Button>
    <Button bordered color="error">
        Error
    </Button>
    <Button bordered color="primary">
        Primary
    </Button>
    <Button bordered color="success">
        Success
    </Button>
    <Button bordered color="black">
        Black
    </Button>
    <Button bordered color="white">
        White
    </Button>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"block"}}>{`Block`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={4} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Button block>Block</Button>`} __scope={{props,Button}}>
    <Button block>
        Block
    </Button>
</Playground></MDXTag>
